PrecisRegulations Amending the GASOLINE REGULATIONS which exempt all competition vehicles from the restrictions on the use of leaded gasoline until December 31, 2002, and will require that all those involved in the production, sale and importation of leaded gasoline retain records and make an annual report on the total amount used in Canada.
